caption.title: DENV virus in the midgut and carcass post DENV infection.
caption.p: A, The DENV titer dynamics in the midgut 10 d.p.i. (post-infection). B, The DENV titer dynamics in the carcass 10 d.p.i. C, The DENV titer dynamics in the midgut post infection. D, DENV titer dynamics in the carcass post infection. Each treatment group comprised 30 mosquitoes. Identical letters are not significant difference ( p > 0.05), while different letters indicate significant difference ( p < 0.05) determined by one way ANOVA followed by a Tukey’s multiple comparison test. All experiments were repeated in triplicate. Data are represented as mean ± SEM.
